psql_query: select firstname, lastname, city, state from person as p left outer join address as a on p.personid = a.personid
select distinct firstname, lastname, city, state from person as p left outer join address as a on p.personid = a.personid;
select distinct a.firstname, a.lastname, b.city, b.state from person as a left outer join address as b on a.personid = b.personid;
select firstname, lastname, city, state from person left outer join address on person.personid = address.personid where person.personid > 0;
select firstname, lastname, city, state from person as p left outer join address as a on p.personid = a.personid group by 1, 2, 3, 4;
